WEBVTT

00:00.950 --> 00:02.721
We are only to happy

00:02.746 --> 00:05.138
to receive Rome's favored son.

00:05.299 --> 00:06.982
The manufacture of armaments

00:07.007 --> 00:09.131
could be construed as
a provocative move.

00:09.136 --> 00:11.672
I believe there may be a spy
in my court.

00:11.741 --> 00:13.483
If we have something
to convey to you,

00:13.508 --> 00:17.202
we will inscribe
the letter Omega.

00:17.348 --> 00:20.690
Tell your Pope that
neither Florence

00:20.715 --> 00:23.451
nor Da Vinci
will be contained.

00:25.523 --> 00:27.591
Whatever lock
this corresponds with,

00:27.658 --> 00:31.062
I'd wager the key represents
only half.

00:31.130 --> 00:33.031
The key is useless
without its counterpart.

00:33.099 --> 00:35.367
Have you heard of
the Book of Leaves?

00:35.435 --> 00:37.770
It's a myth.
No more real than a unicorn.

00:37.838 --> 00:41.375
You and Salviati should assemble
the largest army you can find.

00:41.443 --> 00:45.012
Get to work, maestro.
Florence is counting on you.

00:47.716 --> 00:52.755
♪

